🌍 IR Insights – International Relations Student Platform
📌 About the Project
IR Insights is a platform designed for students of International Relations (IR).
It provides articles, research-based analysis, and discussions on:
Global Securityj
Foreign Policy
Geopolitics
International Organizations
Contemporary Global Affairs
The purpose of this platform is to simplify complex international issues for students and encourage analytical thinking.
🎯 Objectives
To keep IR students updated with global developments
To promote academic research and critical analysis
To provide a space for intellectual discussion
🚀 Future Plans
